users

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • users.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Attendee, Organizer, Speaker

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A user i n the conference program. The User type user only has basic functions and parameters. Most users would fall under one of its child class types: Attendee, Organizer, or Speaker
    See Also:
